V.I.B.E. â€” Domains Layer
Purpose: V.I.B.E. (often framed as Visual Intelligent Build Environment in your docs) is the orchestration and simulation layer. The â€œDomainsâ€ part refers to the logical spaces or contexts it manages â€” each domain is essentially a scoped environment where agents, workflows, and assets can operate without stepping on each other.

What it does:

Hosts visual, composable orchestration of multiâ€‘agent workflows.

