Connect â€” Deploy Layer
Purpose: Connect is the bridge from your orchestrated/simulated environment into the real world â€” the deployment and integration layer. Itâ€™s where a finished build leaves the safe confines of V.I.B.E. and gets pushed to its target environment(s).

What it does:

Handles secure, realâ€‘time integration with external systems (APIs, cloud services, onâ€‘prem targets).

Manages deployment pipelines â€” from packaging artifacts to provisioning infrastructure.

Supports multiâ€‘target deploys â€” e.g., pushing the same build to a staging Shopify store, a production Next.js app, and a partnerâ€™s sandbox.

Maintains deployment provenance â€” logs exactly what went where, when, and with which config.

