Packager agents â€” bundle code, assets, and configs into deployable units (Capsules).

Transport agents â€” handle the actual push to remote targets, with retries and rollback.

Verifier agents â€” run postâ€‘deploy checks (health endpoints, UI smoke tests, asset integrity).

Notifier agents â€” update contributors or systems when a deploy completes or fails.

